 Trading & Positions

  | Feature                | Description                                            |
  |------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|
  | Trailing Stop Loss     | Auto-adjust SL as price moves in your favor            |
  | Break-even button      | One-click to move SL to entry price                    |
  | Partial TP levels      | Set multiple TP targets (TP1: 50%, TP2: 30%, TP3: 20%) |
  | Position alerts        | Browser/sound notifications when PnL hits threshold    |
  | Copy trade to accounts | Open same position across multiple accounts            |
  | Risk/Reward display    | Show R:R ratio on positions based on SL/TP             |

  Dashboard & Analytics

  | Feature               | Description                                           |
  |-----------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
  | Daily PnL summary     | Show today's realized + unrealized PnL                |
  | Win rate stats        | Display win/loss ratio, average win vs average loss   |
  | Equity curve chart    | Graph account balance over time                       |
  | Calendar heatmap      | Show profitable/losing days like GitHub contributions |
  | Drawdown tracker      | Current and max drawdown from peak                    |
  | Trading session stats | Performance by time of day (Asian/London/NY)          |

  Quick Trade Improvements

  | Feature          | Description                                  |
  |------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | More indicators  | RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands for entry signals |
  | Backtest results | Show historical performance of the strategy  |
  | Signal alerts    | Notify when EMA crossover happens            |
  | Auto-trade mode  | Execute trades automatically on signal       |

  Quality of Life

  | Feature                 | Description                                             |
  |-------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|
  | Dark/Light theme toggle | User preference for theme                               |
  | Keyboard shortcuts      | Quick actions (R=refresh, N=new trade, Esc=close modal) |
  | Price alerts            | Set alerts for specific price levels                    |
  | Export trades to CSV    | Download trade history for analysis                     |
  | Mobile PWA improvements | Better offline support, push notifications              |
  | Multi-account overview  | Combined balance/PnL across all accounts                |

  Journal & Review

  | Feature                | Description                                             |
  |------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|
  | Screenshot attachment  | Attach chart screenshots to trades                      |
  | Trade replay           | Review past trades with price action                    |
  | Weekly/Monthly reports | Auto-generated performance summaries                    |
  | Setup tagging          | Link trades to specific setups, track setup performance |

  Risk Management

  | Feature                | Description                               |
  |------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
  | Daily loss limit       | Lock trading after hitting max daily loss |
  | Position size warnings | Alert if size exceeds risk rules          |
  | Correlation check      | Warn when opening correlated positions    |
  | Margin usage display   | Show % of margin used across accounts     |
